.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=branamanstarbinder>Branaman Starbinder</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/15/03 1:52 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3222.topic&index=1>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://httpd.chello.nl/j.wensveen1/images/ofo2.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Balancing</span><hr size=1> well, beside the fact that not each class can solo each type of mob, they are limited to certain types after all, they have to pay in time for their solo skills to. Luckily spells as KEI are available for casters to drop their downtime from 11 minutes after a fight to 6 minutes and then gear kicks in. Of course there are level ranges where the rules change a little.<br>
