ld be able to use ANY weapon in the game except for class epics.  Nothing pisses me off more than a 41/25 1HS we cant use or even a 26/24 1HS.  If warriors had weapons to duel weld with that dam/dly ratio, maybe we would have a chance to keep agro while all you nuke happy 2-4k damage every 5-10 seconds casters with your high hp and high damages pets are beating the hell out of the mobs would  not be stealing agro. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Just a thought.  The fixes are EZ for SoE, if they would just look it them from a warriors eyes. <br>
